name: Nandi Sisters #3
description:
Nandi sisters is the 4th and last solo collection which fits into the Afro-Verse vision.

Whitelist = African Royalty, African Queen Mother, and Afro King holders

Mint price for whitelist = 10 STX (2 pieces per wallet)
Public = 15 STX
Airdrop = 11 pieces
Dev team = 10 pieces

When we started this journey the aim was to just create art with the release of 5 1/1 African Royalty (Paying homage to South African tribal kings). 
Next on the line was African Queen Mother, a 50 pieces collection celebrating the queens of Africa with a modern twist.
This was followed by Afro Kings, which was a 5 STX collection we did overnight.

Up until here, there was a huge problem. We liked creating art but there was no utility. Upon investigating different ideas from an African digital library to games we decided the optimal first step to bring utility would be to release a game that combines all these collections with intriguing storytelling. We then expanded our team to 3 people and started learning code (which we still are).
The ETA on the game as some development work is outsourced is the end of June. However, in between that time, we will launch free 3D variants for every piece of African Queen Mother, African Royalty, Afro King, and Nandi Sisters

This is our road to utility and we are here to stay

Gamma welcomes artists and creators to join us in building the future of digital collectibles.
